  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK870">
<l>kallāṉ vekuḷuñ ciṟuporu ḷeññāṉṟu </l>
<l>mollāṉai yollā toḷi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The light (of fame) will never be gained by him who gains not the trifling reputation of having fought an unlearned (foe).</l>
            </lg>
